Our mission is not only to make our students become good fighters and improve physically, but also to evolve emotionally and mentally. Our martial arts training is designed to help you achieve a new level of discipline and self-defense skills, which empower you to help yourself and others. At Champion Tae Kwon Do, students can learn to compete locally, nationally and even internationally. Work at your own pace and feel the burn while you build endurance, self-discipline, flexibility, and stress control.

Shaolin Martial Arts Center is dedicated to the mental and physical growth of their students through the training of authentic martial arts.  At the school we teach our students to attain a sense of discipline to oneself and respect for others around them.

Ito's White Tiger Dojo has been offering classes and private instruction in the martial arts since 1979. Ito's White Tiger Dojo is a family owned martial arts studio focused on the discipline of the mind, body and spirit. Special introduction and family rates are available. We provide instruction for men, women and children.

Tang Soo Do is derived from the Tang dynasty of China. Soo means hand, and Do means way of life, or art. Tang Soo Do is primarily a China influenced martial art and literal interpretation is The Way of the China Hand. Tang Soo Do implies self defense by a means of the hand and feet without the use of artificial weapons.

Manna's has been a pillar in the martial arts community for over two decades. We offer age specific classes for families and individuals to enjoy the benefits of physical fitness with self-defense training.

Aikido is a Japanese martial art created by Morihei Ueshiba (1883 - 1969).  He is more commonly referred to as O-Sensei (great master).  His ultimate goal was to know the True Self through training in martial arts.  Training in Aikido encompasses not only technique, but also the journey to Self-realization, where our perception of who we truly are turns from the ego to a more universal state of being.  From there a world of peace, found on a powerful stance of love, is actualized.
